data.title: Open Society Foundations - Offices & Foundations
data.meta_description: Our network includes national and regional foundations, as well as programs with regional or global reach, operating in more than 120 countries, including hubs in Europe and the United States.
data.text: By entering your email address and clicking “Submit,” you agree to receive updates from the Open Society Foundations about our work. To learn more about how we use and protect your personal data, please view our privacy policy.
